message.text:
Celebrate 𝑾𝒐𝒓𝒍𝒅 𝑻𝒐𝒖𝒓𝒊𝒔𝒎 𝑫𝒂𝒚 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with us!

Join us on 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟮𝟯, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱, 𝗳𝗿𝗼𝗺 𝟭:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝘁𝗼 𝟱:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝗮𝘁 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗠𝗮𝗶𝗻 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗼𝗿𝗶𝘂𝗺 as we highlight 𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with the theme of "𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑛𝑠𝑓𝑜𝑟𝑚𝑖𝑛𝑔 𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑣𝑒𝑙 𝑖𝑛𝑡𝑜 𝑆𝑢𝑠𝑡𝑎𝑖𝑛𝑎𝑏𝑙𝑒 𝑎𝑛𝑑 𝑀𝑒𝑎𝑛𝑖𝑛𝑔𝑓𝑢𝑙 𝑇𝑜𝑢𝑟𝑖𝑠𝑚." 

Get ready to learn and take bold steps to transform travel into sustainability and meaningful tourism. We have guest speakers to share and advocate their views and expertise into making a sustainable journey and creating meaningful memories. 

Participants will receive e-certificate after the event.

𝙎𝙘𝙖𝙣 𝙩𝙝𝙚 𝙌𝙍 𝙘𝙤𝙙𝙚 or through this link (https://forms.office.com/r/PhxMagSrwp) to 𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙚𝙧. 𝙋𝙧𝙚-𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙧𝙖𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣 𝙤𝙥𝙚𝙣s 𝙪𝙣𝙩𝙞𝙡 𝙎𝙖𝙩𝙪𝙧𝙙𝙖𝙮, 7:00 𝙋𝙈

Don’t miss this exciting event and be part of a global celebration that inspires change and shapes the future of tourism. As one, let’s take the next step towards a more sustainable and meaningful journey. See you there!

#WorldTourismDay2025
#SustainableTourism 
#FEU
#FEU97th
#FEUITHM
#EventuraProduction

message.text:
Celebrate 𝑾𝒐𝒓𝒍𝒅 𝑻𝒐𝒖𝒓𝒊𝒔𝒎 𝑫𝒂𝒚 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with us!

Join us on 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟮𝟯, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱, 𝗳𝗿𝗼𝗺 𝟭:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝘁𝗼 𝟱:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝗮𝘁 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗠𝗮𝗶𝗻 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗼𝗿𝗶𝘂𝗺 as we highlight 𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with the theme of "𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑛𝑠𝑓𝑜𝑟𝑚𝑖𝑛𝑔 𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑣𝑒𝑙 𝑖𝑛𝑡𝑜 𝑆𝑢𝑠𝑡𝑎𝑖𝑛𝑎𝑏𝑙𝑒 𝑎𝑛𝑑 𝑀𝑒𝑎𝑛𝑖𝑛𝑔𝑓𝑢𝑙 𝑇𝑜𝑢𝑟𝑖𝑠𝑚." 

Get ready to learn and take bold steps to transform travel into sustainability and meaningful tourism. We have guest speakers to share and advocate their views and expertise into making a sustainable journey and creating meaningful memories. 

Participants will receive e-certificate after the event.

𝙎𝙘𝙖𝙣 𝙩𝙝𝙚 𝙌𝙍 𝙘𝙤𝙙𝙚 or through this link (https://forms.office.com/r/PhxMagSrwp) to 𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙚𝙧. 𝙋𝙧𝙚-𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙧𝙖𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣 𝙤𝙥𝙚𝙣s 𝙪𝙣𝙩𝙞𝙡 𝙎𝙖𝙩𝙪𝙧𝙙𝙖𝙮, 7:00 𝙋𝙈

Don’t miss this exciting event and be part of a global celebration that inspires change and shapes the future of tourism. As one, let’s take the next step towards a more sustainable and meaningful journey. See you there!

message.text:
Celebrate 𝑾𝒐𝒓𝒍𝒅 𝑻𝒐𝒖𝒓𝒊𝒔𝒎 𝑫𝒂𝒚 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with us!

Join us on 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟮𝟯, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱, 𝗳𝗿𝗼𝗺 𝟭:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝘁𝗼 𝟱:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝗮𝘁 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗠𝗮𝗶𝗻 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗼𝗿𝗶𝘂𝗺 as we highlight 𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with the theme of "𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑛𝑠𝑓𝑜𝑟𝑚𝑖𝑛𝑔 𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑣𝑒𝑙 𝑖𝑛𝑡𝑜 𝑆𝑢𝑠𝑡𝑎𝑖𝑛𝑎𝑏𝑙𝑒 𝑎𝑛𝑑 𝑀𝑒𝑎𝑛𝑖𝑛𝑔𝑓𝑢𝑙 𝑇𝑜𝑢𝑟𝑖𝑠𝑚." 

Get ready to learn and take bold steps to transform travel into sustainability and meaningful tourism. We have guest speakers to share and advocate their views and expertise into making a sustainable journey and creating meaningful memories. 

Participants will receive e-certificate after the event.

𝙎𝙘𝙖𝙣 𝙩𝙝𝙚 𝙌𝙍 𝙘𝙤𝙙𝙚 or through this link (https://forms.office.com/r/PhxMagSrwp) to 𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙚𝙧. 𝙋𝙧𝙚-𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙧𝙖𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣 𝙤𝙥𝙚𝙣s 𝙪𝙣𝙩𝙞𝙡 𝙎𝙖𝙩𝙪𝙧𝙙𝙖𝙮, 7:00 𝙋𝙈

Don’t miss this exciting event and be part of a global celebration that inspires change and shapes the future of tourism. As one, let’s take the next step towards a more sustainable and meaningful journey. See you there!

Join us on 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟮𝟯, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱, 𝗳𝗿𝗼𝗺 𝟭:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝘁𝗼 𝟱:𝟬𝟬 𝗣𝗠 𝗮𝘁 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗠𝗮𝗶𝗻 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗼𝗿𝗶𝘂𝗺 as we highlight 𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 with the theme of "𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑛𝑠𝑓𝑜𝑟𝑚𝑖𝑛𝑔 𝑇𝑟𝑎𝑣𝑒𝑙 𝑖𝑛𝑡𝑜 𝑆𝑢𝑠𝑡𝑎𝑖𝑛𝑎𝑏𝑙𝑒 𝑎𝑛𝑑 𝑀𝑒𝑎𝑛𝑖𝑛𝑔𝑓𝑢𝑙 𝑇𝑜𝑢𝑟𝑖𝑠𝑚." 

Get ready to learn and take bold steps to transform travel into sustainability and meaningful tourism. We have guest speakers to share and advocate their views and expertise into making a sustainable journey and creating meaningful memories. 

Participants will receive e-certificate after the event.

𝙎𝙘𝙖𝙣 𝙩𝙝𝙚 𝙌𝙍 𝙘𝙤𝙙𝙚 or through this link (https://forms.office.com/r/PhxMagSrwp) to 𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙚𝙧. 𝙋𝙧𝙚-𝙧𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙧𝙖𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣 𝙤𝙥𝙚𝙣s 𝙪𝙣𝙩𝙞𝙡 𝙎𝙖𝙩𝙪𝙧𝙙𝙖𝙮, 7:00 𝙋𝙈

Don’t miss this exciting event and be part of a global celebration that inspires change and shapes the future of tourism. As one, let’s take the next step towards a more sustainable and meaningful journey. See you there!

message.text:
𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐯𝐞𝐥 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐈𝐦𝐩𝐚𝐜𝐭: 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐋𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐖𝐚𝐲! ✈️🌏

𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 presents 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐢𝐧 𝐀𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, an exciting event centered on the theme “𝐄𝐦𝐩𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐧𝐬𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞.” This event highlights how volunteer efforts can create meaningful change in communities and travel experiences worldwide.

Be part of the movement that combines passion for travel with a commitment to giving back. This is your chance to learn, connect, and take action for responsible tourism that uplifts lives and preserves cultures.

message.text:
𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐯𝐞𝐥 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐈𝐦𝐩𝐚𝐜𝐭: 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐋𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐖𝐚𝐲! ✈️🌏

𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 presents 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐢𝐧 𝐀𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, an exciting event centered on the theme “𝐄𝐦𝐩𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐧𝐬𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞.” This event highlights how volunteer efforts can create meaningful change in communities and travel experiences worldwide.

Be part of the movement that combines passion for travel with a commitment to giving back. This is your chance to learn, connect, and take action for responsible tourism that uplifts lives and preserves cultures.

Register now and step into a journey where your time and skills make a lasting difference, PATAms! 

🗓️: 𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟐, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓
🕰️: 𝟏:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 - 𝟒:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 
📍: 𝐒𝐜𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐁𝐮𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝟏𝟎𝟐 - 𝟏𝟎𝟒

𝐑𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐋𝐢𝐧𝐤:
https://forms.gle/8TrXYkVziu7W7oGL8

In partnership with:
FEU ITHM Music Makers
FEU Sexuality and Gender Alliance 
TAMang Boto

Caption by: Ysha Patapat
Pubmat by: Layza Tolomia

#PATAPHFEU
#WTD2025

Be part of the movement that combines passion for travel with a commitment to giving back. This is your chance to learn, connect, and take action for responsible tourism that uplifts lives and preserves cultures.

Register now and step into a journey where your time and skills make a lasting difference, PATAms!

𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 presents 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐢𝐧 𝐀𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, an exciting event centered on the theme “𝐄𝐦𝐩𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐧𝐬𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞.” This event highlights how volunteer efforts can create meaningful change in communities and travel experiences worldwide.

Be part of the movement that combines passion for travel with a commitment to giving back. This is your chance to learn, connect, and take action for responsible tourism that uplifts lives and preserves cultures.

Register now and step into a journey where your time and skills make a lasting difference, PATAms! 

🗓️: 𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟐, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓
🕰️: 𝟏:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 - 𝟒:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 
📍: 𝐒𝐜𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐁𝐮𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝟏𝟎𝟐 - 𝟏𝟎𝟒

𝐑𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐋𝐢𝐧𝐤:
https://forms.gle/8TrXYkVziu7W7oGL8
https://forms.gle/8TrXYkVziu7W7oGL8

In partnership with:
FEU ITHM Music Makers
FEU Sexuality and Gender Alliance 
TAMang Boto

Caption by: Ysha Patapat
Pubmat by: Layza Tolomia

#PATAPHFEU
#WTD2025

message.text:
𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐯𝐞𝐥 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐈𝐦𝐩𝐚𝐜𝐭: 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐋𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐖𝐚𝐲! ✈️🌏

𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 presents 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐢𝐧 𝐀𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, an exciting event centered on the theme “𝐄𝐦𝐩𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐧𝐬𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞.” This event highlights how volunteer efforts can create meaningful change in communities and travel experiences worldwide.

Be part of the movement that combines passion for travel with a commitment to giving back. This is your chance to learn, connect, and take action for responsible tourism that uplifts lives and preserves cultures.

Register now and step into a journey where your time and skills make a lasting difference, PATAms! 

🗓️: 𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟐, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓
🕰️: 𝟏:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 - 𝟒:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 
📍: 𝐒𝐜𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐁𝐮𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝟏𝟎𝟐 - 𝟏𝟎𝟒

𝐑𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐋𝐢𝐧𝐤:
https://forms.gle/8TrXYkVziu7W7oGL8

FEU ITHM Music Makers
FEU Sexuality and Gender Alliance 
TAMang Boto

message.text:
𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐯𝐞𝐥 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐈𝐦𝐩𝐚𝐜𝐭: 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐋𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐖𝐚𝐲! ✈️🌏

𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 presents 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐢𝐧 𝐀𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, an exciting event centered on the theme “𝐄𝐦𝐩𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐧𝐬𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞.” This event highlights how volunteer efforts can create meaningful change in communities and travel experiences worldwide.

Be part of the movement that combines passion for travel with a commitment to giving back. This is your chance to learn, connect, and take action for responsible tourism that uplifts lives and preserves cultures.

Register now and step into a journey where your time and skills make a lasting difference, PATAms! 

🗓️: 𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟐, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓
🕰️: 𝟏:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 - 𝟒:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 
📍: 𝐒𝐜𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐁𝐮𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝟏𝟎𝟐 - 𝟏𝟎𝟒

𝐑𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐋𝐢𝐧𝐤:

message.text:
𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐯𝐞𝐥 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐈𝐦𝐩𝐚𝐜𝐭: 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐋𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐖𝐚𝐲! ✈️🌏

𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 presents 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐢𝐧 𝐀𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, an exciting event centered on the theme “𝐄𝐦𝐩𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐧𝐬𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞.” This event highlights how volunteer efforts can create meaningful change in communities and travel experiences worldwide.

Be part of the movement that combines passion for travel with a commitment to giving back. This is your chance to learn, connect, and take action for responsible tourism that uplifts lives and preserves cultures.

Register now and step into a journey where your time and skills make a lasting difference, PATAms! 

🗓️: 𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟐, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓
🕰️: 𝟏:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 - 𝟒:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 
📍: 𝐒𝐜𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐁𝐮𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝟏𝟎𝟐 - 𝟏𝟎𝟒

𝐑𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐋𝐢𝐧𝐤:
https://forms.gle/8TrXYkVziu7W7oGL8

message.text:
𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐯𝐞𝐥 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐈𝐦𝐩𝐚𝐜𝐭: 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐋𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐖𝐚𝐲! ✈️🌏

𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 presents 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐢𝐧 𝐀𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, an exciting event centered on the theme “𝐄𝐦𝐩𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐧𝐬𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞.” This event highlights how volunteer efforts can create meaningful change in communities and travel experiences worldwide.

Be part of the movement that combines passion for travel with a commitment to giving back. This is your chance to learn, connect, and take action for responsible tourism that uplifts lives and preserves cultures.

Register now and step into a journey where your time and skills make a lasting difference, PATAms! 

🗓️: 𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟐, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓
🕰️: 𝟏:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 - 𝟒:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 
📍: 𝐒𝐜𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐁𝐮𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝟏𝟎𝟐 - 𝟏𝟎𝟒

𝐑𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐋𝐢𝐧𝐤:
https://forms.gle/8TrXYkVziu7W7oGL8
https://forms.gle/8TrXYkVziu7W7oGL8

In partnership with:
FEU ITHM Music Makers
FEU Sexuality and Gender Alliance 
TAMang Boto

Caption by: Ysha Patapat
Pubmat by: Layza Tolomia
